{
  "id": "RAW_cbbd0d05",
  "title": "用 Claude Skills 做 PPT，真实演示",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&mid=2247499265&idx=1&sn=ec4352b48d8b0b292c78bbb4652c4716",
  "date": "2025-10-20 06:46:00",
  "author": "刘小排",
  "siteName": "刘小排r",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span style=\"background-color: inherit; font-size: 1rem;\">大家好，我是小排。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">今天我要解决的一个真实问题： 本周末我要做两天一夜的线下课，要做PPT。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">面对的挑战</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">整整两天一夜啊！那就意味着，我需要做一个超越200页的PPT！</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我已经有讲义的文字稿了，需要分段把讲义文字变成PPT设计。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">每一页内容都需要自己打磨，无法靠gamma或者Manus等AI PPT工具一把梭。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">每一页内容的风格要一致，审美要高级。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">PPT模板是给定的，必须要符合模板风格。</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">正好，现在有了Claude Skills，上述问题就简单了。还不知道什么是Claude Skill的同学，可以看上节课&nbsp;<a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&amp;mid=2247499243&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=f8750d2e3e47f51144cd695ac1337562&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"技术圈吹爆的Claude Skills，小白用起来比程序员还爽\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">技术圈吹爆的Claude Skills，小白用起来比程序员还爽</a></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">下面演示我的实际工作过程。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">整体思路</span></span></p>\n  <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">制定风格</span>：在Claude里聊天，给出我的要求和PPT模板的风格，让Claude试出我满意的风格。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">解决粘贴到PPT模板问题</span>：使用透明PNG。让Claude输出的卡片有“一键变成透明PNG”的功能，这样粘贴到PPT里，可以把背景透出来。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">解决稳定性问题</span>：调试完成后，让Claude把刚才的所有要求封装为一个Skill。以后新开窗口，通知Claude用Skill来创建单页</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <div>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">制定风格</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;list&quot;,{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;ol&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;list-style-type: decimal&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;list-paddingleft-1&quot;,&quot;start&quot;:null},&quot;listitem&quot;,{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">让我先选取了模板风格，纯粹文字和Claude对话</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015610\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9015151515151515\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"792\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4ba46874&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGpF5d51UM7WN3YMibk9ib2n9Up8oIFcNnMOibMe1icjvEs0BL55NsEBSD5CdDcOPyEGDr1In9K2fmPcA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;list&quot;,{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;ol&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;list-style-type: decimal&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;list-paddingleft-1&quot;,&quot;start&quot;:null},&quot;listitem&quot;,{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">刚出来的第一版，我不喜欢，如下图所示。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;list&quot;,{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;ol&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;list-style-type: decimal&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;list-paddingleft-1&quot;,&quot;start&quot;:null},&quot;listitem&quot;,{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">不过没关系，我可以继续和它聊天调整，直到满意为止。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015611\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5388888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c541fc9a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGpF5d51UM7WN3YMibk9ib2n9FaBjS90L3C3oaPPuWyWpymK7vTbLxjSUCVWnbqHyb4E4nxoGJ5LktA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;list&quot;,{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;ol&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;list-style-type: decimal&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;list-paddingleft-1&quot;,&quot;start&quot;:null},&quot;listitem&quot;,{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">反复打磨后，看到这样的效果，我感觉可以接受了</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015596\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5425925925925926\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=87ddac0f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGpF5d51UM7WN3YMibk9ib2n9Cep3KiaVmI6Pcg7hGRh54o9cZyHMH7xZUJQa9TlbWONAEgHkNRbyJHQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">变成Skill</span></span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">风格打磨完成后，告诉Claude：变成一个Skill。它会继续引导我们。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015612\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8898148148148148\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f8fec7fd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGpF5d51UM7WN3YMibk9ib2n9UaDVMQpJwW46fmnQ2swQ8lK1kFq3qdgSo99ocibibrbyLD1I7ibTUia5dA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015613\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9529702970297029\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1616\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=97d0f6b2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGpF5d51UM7WN3YMibk9ib2n9icIpZGTFl79V0TuLBvLiaVWAic4kX2r7wYJyBZk3vwbX6h8h5RF2kqicoQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">记得下载安装</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015614\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7648148148148148\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4a2be8fe&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGpF5d51UM7WN3YMibk9ib2n9bTPnjq6WIxib8JWUZzIiaj0ZQibxxYbEUiaAXctre8bX6Hiaz5xvNrQDbwg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015598\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.24166666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dc02e246&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGpF5d51UM7WN3YMibk9ib2n9ic9YxhYuS5I7bsEFVYecfsDupbNZSnqicXIyLsoO0yAwq9NzuiaMUdyUw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">不知道如何安装的同学，请继续复习上节课&nbsp;<a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&amp;mid=2247499243&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=f8750d2e3e47f51144cd695ac1337562&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"技术圈吹爆的Claude Skills，小白用起来比程序员还爽\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">技术圈吹爆的Claude Skills，小白用起来比程序员还爽</a></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">使用Skill</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">新开一个聊天窗口，告诉它，用Skill来设计。</span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015599\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6851851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7615d29b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGpF5d51UM7WN3YMibk9ib2n9JvNsFa6VGkwOO7M7RibHubE28SYCI5eicO4icSry3ubQpCdIAMFID6s7g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">它可以稳定发挥</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015604\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5314814814814814\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2c6b0bd5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGpF5d51UM7WN3YMibk9ib2n9YEo5cK0TM8XjLXGgyXUvyAHYbqt3jfCYzhGyKfq1aQ76rd6wrX0O9w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015607\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5342592592592592\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4b6e3d00&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGpF5d51UM7WN3YMibk9ib2n9kK9JNwdfwGYt4U8hJsjPiblcNvZRAia6uhhvoM0qahibpBicfT87Xnqm2g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">怎么样？是不是既符合苹果的设计风格、又有我要求的主题颜色？</span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\">点击“复制透明PNG”</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015609\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0fd89870&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGpF5d51UM7WN3YMibk9ib2n9rMQMTS1Vpc4ooVJUaXbBc7ibCNnFZTyKic1ibv0ib9BwJEHDI5crEnvVDQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015605\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"3200\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d1a946a4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGpF5d51UM7WN3YMibk9ib2n9O0R9Dg5IZCuXAuoRgkWrib54mkfEE3xOcY9vH7maFLXG1tX2NjUzcTQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">把透明PNG粘贴到模板里，感觉挺合适的！</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015606\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.38333333333333336\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=96b4c0ea&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGpF5d51UM7WN3YMibk9ib2n9l8yDk5zm6NhhAhX7ibOdN7a4VJDwt4Cd0jC1RoQyZ6xlle8geiaIgEdQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015608\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3861111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b99df5e4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGpF5d51UM7WN3YMibk9ib2n9v1Hiaj4ibfwJCyZGibVqWHF6mgzHWFia1H0KMXrGFPrFNufGgljgVnrvAw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">期待你的反馈！</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">下课！</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文详细演示了如何利用 Claude Skills 结合透明 PNG 技术，高效且定制化地生成符合特定风格的 PPT 单页，以解决大规模演示文稿制作难题。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文详细演示了如何利用 Claude Skills 结合透明 PNG 技术，高效且定制化地生成符合特定风格的 PPT 单页，以解决大规模演示文稿制作难题。",
  "summary": "文章针对制作大量、高定制化 PPT 的真实痛点，提出了基于 Claude Skills 的解决方案。作者面临为两天一夜线下课制作超过 200 页 PPT 的挑战，并强调了内容精细打磨、风格一致性及模板适配的重要性，认为传统 AI PPT 工具难以满足这些需求。文章核心思路包括：首先，通过与 Claude 多轮对话，精心调试并确定满意的 PPT 单页视觉风格；其次，创新性地利用透明 PNG 格式输出，解决了 AI 生成内容与现有 PPT 模板的无缝集成问题；最后，将这些定制化要求封装为 Claude Skill，确保了后续 PPT 页面生成的高度稳定性和复用性。文章通过实际操作演示，展现了该方法在提升 PPT 制作效率和质量方面的显著效果。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "利用 Claude Skills 可实现高度定制化的 PPT 单页设计与风格统一",
      "explanation": "通过与 Claude 进行迭代式对话和调试，用户能够精确定义 PPT 的视觉风格和内容布局，并将这一风格固化为 Skill，确保后续生成页面的高度一致性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "结合透明 PNG 输出能有效解决 AI 生成内容与现有 PPT 模板的集成问题",
      "explanation": "文章创新性地提出让 Claude 输出透明 PNG 格式的卡片，用户可以直接粘贴到预设的 PPT 模板中，避免了背景冲突和格式调整，显著简化了集成流程。"
    },
    {
      "point": "将定制化需求封装为 Skill，显著提升了 AI 工具使用的稳定性和复用性",
      "explanation": "一旦特定的设计要求被固化为 Skill，用户在新会话中可以一键调用，确保每次输出都符合预期，极大提升了工作效率和输出质量的稳定性。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "整整两天一夜啊！那就意味着，我需要做一个超越 200 页的 PPT！",
